comments: He\'s funny, and one of the best math instructors I\'ve ever had. I appreciated his dedication.

This is the first time I have ever been able to understand math. He is a great teacher , I wish more teachers taught li he does. He takes his time and makes sure you understand the work. Also he is very funny and keeps the class from being dull or hard. He keeps it very interesting and is a very understanding teacher. we need more teachers like him
Awesome professor!!!!!! I would recommend him to anybody! !!!

I had Prof Avidano for Developmental Arithmetic this past semester and I have nothing but great things to say about him! His way of explaining math is awesome, he makes it seem so simple and won\'t move on until you understand. He is also really hilarious and an all around nice guy!
The best math teacher I\'ve ever encountered. Cares about his students learning.
The best math teacher Ive ever had!!!Makes sure everyone unerstands....very caring...
